to please me. Well done.

564
00:40:37,460 --> 00:40:38,860
Your Ladyship, I…

565
00:40:38,860 --> 00:40:41,500
Don't be afraid.
I didn't say I'd punish you.

566
00:40:42,540 --> 00:40:46,820
I just want to warn you
not to eavesdrop anymore.

567
00:40:47,220 --> 00:40:50,980
If you think you can trick me,
you are sadly mistaken.

568
00:40:51,700 --> 00:40:53,060
Thank you for your forgiveness.

569
00:40:53,420 --> 00:40:54,980
I didn't do it on purpose.

570
00:40:55,420 --> 00:40:57,460
On purpose or not, it doesn't matter.

571
00:40:58,100 --> 00:41:02,460
But, I can see your appreciation
towards Gu Jin is real.

572
00:41:02,740 --> 00:41:04,540
I dare not have improper thoughts.

573
00:41:05,220 --> 00:41:08,740
Thoughts are thoughts, improper or not.

574
00:41:09,500 --> 00:41:11,860
Our Gu Jin came to
the Three Realms for a trial.

575
00:41:12,100 --> 00:41:17,060
If someone truly loves him,
I won't get in the way.

576
00:41:18,540 --> 00:41:22,660
But whether you'll be that someone
depends on your destiny.

577
00:41:27,580 --> 00:41:28,940
I can see you are a smart girl.

578
00:41:29,300 --> 00:41:33,540
In the future, if Gu Jin needs any help,
I hope he can have your support.

579
00:41:36,820 --> 00:41:39,820
Alright, I'm tired. You can go now.

